# AAIS Precedence

Canonical: [META_ARCHITECT_LAWBOOK.md](../../META_ARCHITECT_LAWBOOK.md)

## Order (highest wins)

Law → Blueprint → Contract → Implementation → Pipeline → Tool

## CI vs lawbook

- Pipelines **enforce**; they do **not** authorize
- Passing CI does not supersede constitutional requirements (Doctrine VII)
- No CI bypass for required governance gates

